  {
    "uuid": "abc6994e-0e21-5dba-9b31-76eee69d1957",
    "entry": "璆鏘",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "きゅうそう",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "形容詞-たる",
        "副詞-と"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "echoing beautifully (of the sound produced by striking together jewels or metals)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "玉と玉が触れ合う璆鏘たる響きが、しんとした静寂の広間に美しく通った。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「この鐘の音は、まるで宝石を打つように璆鏘としていて、心が洗われるようだね」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "古代の王族たちは、身につけた金属の飾りが璆鏘と鳴る音を歩くたびに楽しんだという。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "その楽器の音色は璆鏘として澄み渡り、聴く者を遠い異国の地へと誘う。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
    ],
