  {
    "uuid": "e2691fa2-a282-544a-b09d-3273368d04bf",
    "entry": "穹蒼",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "きゅうそう",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "dome of the sky",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "どこまでも深く蒼い穹蒼を見上げていると、自分の悩みがちっぽけなものに思えてきた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "一羽の鷲が、広大な穹蒼を悠々と旋回しながら獲物を探している。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "日が沈み、穹蒼は次第に燃えるような茜色から深い紺色へと染まっていった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「見てごらん、今日の穹蒼は雲一つなくて、まるで吸い込まれそうな青さだよ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
    ],
